nodes.text: Sector Epsilon 51-3 was a sector in First Order territory, which they kept off-limits to others. During the occupation of Castilon's Colossus platform, Commander Pyre led stormtroopers to arrest Team Fireball after receiving a report that the team's namesake, the Fireball, had been seen participating in a Resistance mission into the sector that found clues hinting at the existence of Starkiller Base.
